  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Heavy marijuana users report experiencing trouble sleeping when they try to quit, but this
      has not been carefully studied. This research is being done to learn more about sleep
      function in heavy marijuana users, and to determine whether a medication approved for
      treating insomnia can help restore normal sleep function during brief periods of abstinence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
